body:
Hi @andrewharp ,

Thanks for your effort for making the new android demo project, but could you please write a readme.md or some description document in [tensorflow/contrib/lite/examples/android](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/examples/android) so that we could all easily understand the process to make tensorflow lite? thanks~!
